---
export const prerender = true;
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Delete Your Account" description="How to delete your Convocados account and all associated data.">
  <h1>Delete Your Account</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">How to permanently delete your account and all associated data.</p>

  <h2>What gets deleted</h2>
  <p>When you delete your account, the following data is <strong>permanently removed</strong>:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your profile (name, email, profile picture)</li>
    <li>Your login credentials and sessions</li>
    <li>Your notification preferences and push tokens</li>
    <li>Your API keys</li>
    <li>Your calendar tokens</li>
    <li>Your player claims (linked players become anonymous)</li>
    <li>Your event ownership (events become unowned)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How to delete your account</h2>

  <h3>From the mobile app</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Open the Convocados app</li>
    <li>Go to your <strong>Profile</strong> (tap your avatar or the profile icon)</li>
    <li>Scroll down and tap <strong>"Delete Account"</strong></li>
    <li>Confirm the deletion when prompted</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>From the web app</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Sign in at <a href="https://convocados.fly.dev">convocados.fly.dev</a></li>
    <li>Click your name in the top-right corner to open your profile</li>
    <li>Scroll down and click <strong>"Delete Account"</strong></li>
    <li>Confirm the deletion when prompted</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Important notes</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Account deletion is <strong>immediate and irreversible</strong></li>
    <li>Game history you participated in will be anonymized (your name removed from records)</li>
    <li>Events you created will remain but will no longer have an owner</li>
    <li>Other players will no longer see your name in past games</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Need help?</h2>
  <p>
    If you cannot access your account to delete it, or need assistance,
    please open an issue on our <a href="https://github.com/Cabeda/Convocados/issues">GitHub repository</a>
    with your account email and we will process the deletion manually.
  </p>
</DocsLayout>
